COMBAT.ARMOUR.LIGHT
 "~CLABMoving about in light armour~CHLP"
 ~CBRTDifficulty: ~CHLPeasy
 ~CBRTStats Used: ~CHLPdex, str

~CHLPThis skill reduces your penalties for wearing light armour and is completely independant of skill with heavy armour. Some leather and hide equipment is classified as light as are most types of mail. Heavy clothing does not usually require this skill.

